The `return_connection()` method is called from Drop, which cannot return errors. For that specific case, use `unwrap_or_else` with logging:
```rust
match self.shared.inner.lock() {
    Ok(mut inner) => { /* return connection */ }
    Err(_) => {
        tracing::error!("Pool mutex poisoned; connection leaked");
    }
}
```

